               <p>JOHN BURTON. I live opposite. There was a mattrass found in my house, which was claimed by Mr. Barrowcliff; that mattrass I received from the prisoner, who on a former occasion had borrowed a mattrass from me, as I understand for his master, and he gave me the one in question as an equivalent.</p>

               <p>
            
